OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRemaining
OL,6,Ffine and dry this evening with some
OL,7,Flate sunshine. Patchy cloud will tend
OL,8,Fto develop overnight with a few mist
OL,9,Fand patches also forming, especially
OL,10,Fin prone valleys.
OL,11,
OL,12,CWednesday:FAnother dry and fine day
OL,13,Facross Wales, with the best of the
OL,14,Fsunshine towards the south. Feeling
OL,15,Fwarm once again.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
